{"tid":2124944,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"讀緊學店 好迷惘","createTime":"2020-07-25T20:40:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-26T05:28:54.000Z","uid":352292,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d28532c1fc959390d4b42c98becb59d1d6b04e7e","tid":2124944,"uid":352292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T20:40:13.000Z","msg":"新手出po 屌細力啲<br />\n<br />\n講下背景：<br />\n2018年考DSE Best 5 加埋得18 (43443)<br />\n自問讀書唔係叻 家底又唔係好 就唔敢asso/retake<br />\n最尾就on99咁揀咗thei測量 讀咗兩年升year 3 CGPA2.83<br />\n<br />\n起初仲以為學店真係workready 諗住fg都可以搵到份工做下<br />\n但後尾愈讀愈覺得唔掂 同Poly/KongU/City啲中同比差好多<br />\n諗到到時出到嚟可能冇人認受自已 <br />\n就諗係唔係應該當自己gap year 咗兩年 再去retake<br />\n定係chur GPA 到時搵master(非學店)讀幫自已洗底會好啲<br />\n<br />\n求點醒/屌醒"},{"pid":"6c3b97d9b62ed592f8e7409e7d6beb311a66d0b8","tid":2124944,"uid":359022,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T20:49:46.000Z","msg":"chur GPA 搵master"},{"pid":"5abb99ce3af9aa7f240e37c9f86cc97fda717bf4","tid":2124944,"uid":235370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d28532c1fc959390d4b42c98becb59d1d6b04e7e","tid":2124944,"uid":352292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T20:40:13.000Z","msg":"新手出po 屌細力啲<br />\n<br />\n講下背景：<br />\n2018年考DSE Best 5 加埋得18 (43443)<br />\n自問讀書唔係叻 家底又唔係好 就唔敢asso/retake<br />\n最尾就on99咁揀咗thei測量 讀咗兩年升year 3 CGPA2.83<br />\n<br />\n起初仲以為學店真係workready 諗住fg都可以搵到份工做下<br />\n但後尾愈讀愈覺得唔掂 同Poly/KongU/City啲中同比差好多<br />\n諗到到時出到嚟可能冇人認受自已 <br />\n就諗係唔係應該當自己gap year 咗兩年 再去retake<br />\n定係chur GPA 到時搵master(非學店)讀幫自已洗底會好啲<br />\n<br />\n求點醒/屌醒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T20:50:02.000Z","msg":"你最後想做咩行業先，有啲行業讀咗碩士都未必cover到讀碩士嘅錢"},{"pid":"d73a8b29adec8aa94bbe4ba56102a7122b3df422","tid":2124944,"uid":352292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5abb99ce3af9aa7f240e37c9f86cc97fda717bf4","tid":2124944,"uid":235370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d28532c1fc959390d4b42c98becb59d1d6b04e7e","tid":2124944,"uid":352292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor